content:
What would be the JavaScript code to create a detailed description of a new smartphone in HTML format? The description should include the brand, model, screen size, resolution, processor, RAM, storage, battery capacity, camera specifications, operating system, and connectivity options. Please use the following data:
var brand = "Samsung";
var model = "Galaxy S21";
var screenSize = "6.2 inches";
var resolution = "1080 x 2400 pixels";
var processor = "Exynos 2100";
var RAM = "8 GB";
var storage = "128 GB";
var batteryCapacity = "4000 mAh";
var camera = "Triple Camera (12 MP + 64 MP + 12 MP)";
var OS = "Android 11";
var connectivity = "5G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 5.2, NFC";
Please ensure the output is formatted in a clean and organized way.
